SUMMARY:Deadline: Exygy: Senior Product Designer (Bloom\, temporary)
DESCRIPTION:Exygy is hiring a temporary Senior Product Designer (UX/UI) to 
 work on Bloom\, its affordable-housing platform. Remote within the United 
 States. Compensation: $97\,750-$132\,250 per year. Engagement runs Q3 2026
  to Q1 2027. NOTE: this is a job\, not a grant or fellowship. Application 
 deadline Monday\, 8 June 2026.\n\nOrganisation: Exygy\nLocation: Remote\, 
 United States\nAward: Paid role: $97\,750-$132\,250 per year for a tempora
 ry engagement. No application fee.\nDuration: Temporary engagement Q3 2026
  to Q1 2027\n\nMore: https://exygy.com/careers/
URL:https://exygy.com/careers/
LOCATION:Remote\, United States
